reviewText: This dvd has some season 1 epsiodes as long as some bonus features. It has episodes big time blogger, terror, dance, sparks, fever, video, and concert. The special feautes include the house of anubis pilot episode and behind the scenes (which are very funn). If your a fan of big time rush then I would recommend this dvd.
summary: DVD for big time rush fans
